I heard one EVP from them that made me laugh out loud. It went  
something like this:

&quot;Bill?&quot;
&quot;Jeff?
&quot;Jeff. Susan?&quot;
&quot;Susan. Bill?&quot;
&quot;Bill.&quot;
&quot;Susan. Jeff?&quot;
&quot;Jeff.&quot;
&quot;Bill.&quot;

It reminded me of the who&#39;s on first routine by Abbott and Costello.

Ann

